article_id:1763,category_name:News,title_name:Regarding Issues with Gala Reborn Poseidon,image_path:,message:<div>We have confirmed that the following issues were occurring with the dragon Gala Reborn Poseidon, who was added to a summon showcase at <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1604037600"></span>.</div><div><br></div><div>・Normal attack power while shapeshifted was lower than intended.</div><div>・The Atlantean Flood skill&#39;s power was lower than intended.</div><div><br></div><div>These issues have been fixed in a data update applied at approximately <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1604468400"></span>.</div><div><br></div><div>Thank you for playing Dragalia Lost.</div>,start_time:1604468400,update_time1605603084